IP-CIDR,1.1.1.1/32,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,1.0.0.1/32,no-resolve

# Cisco OpenDNS
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,opendns.com
IP-CIDR,146.112.41.2/32,no-resolve

